_sText:
"A map I started on at Xmas. Work on it has pretty much ground to a halt since I started my new job so I thought I would post up as far as I got.

Known Issues:
Soundscape & point sound problems.
Not properly optimised.
Sketchy texturing.
Models ain't all that either.
Displacements are a bit blocky.

C&C welcome. I am interested in whether people think the map is balanced, if there is enough cover, good lines of sight, too sniper dominated etc.
